PARIS -- French President Jacques Chirac Wednesday called on
the armed forces of his country to "maintain the course" of
national defense reform. (France-National Defense)
</P>
<P>
KIGALI -- Forty people were murdered in two Rwandan communes of
Central Gitarama Prefecture early this week, officials in the area
told the Rwanda News Agency Wednesday. (Rwanda-Killings) 
