floating rate funds. The sole lead manager is Goldman Sachs (Asia)
LLC.
</P>
<P>
The latest transaction brings IFC's market borrowing to about
1,910 million dollars for the fiscal year 1998, which began on
July 1, 1997.
</P>
<P>
IFC is a member of the World Bank Group and is the largest
multilateral source of financing for private sector projects in
developing countries. 
