The search-and-rescue exercise code-named "Reliant Mermaid" was
held today, despite condemnation from neighboring Arab countries.
</P>
<P>
Two Turkish frigates, a U.S. destroyer with two helicopters
and four Israeli vessels participated in the maneuver. 
