five years ago, when he worked behind the scenes to keep the
Israeli and Palestine Liberation Organization negotiators on
target.
</P>
<P>
Larsen's appointment put him in the same league as U.S.
peace coordinator Dennis Ross and European Union peace envoy
Miguel Moratinos insofar as the international effort to help
bring the peace process back on track.
</P>
<P>
Ross is now on his shuttle diplomacy between Israel and
the Palestinian National Authority (PNA) to work out the plans
of Israel's troop pullback in the West Bank. But so far no
progress was made in this regard.
</P>
<P>
Ross is scheduled to meet Netanyahu later in the evening
again after holding talks with PNA Chairman Yasser Arafat.
