European Union (EU), and pointed out the broad prospects for
Sino-EU relations based on the strong complimentary ties between
the two sides. He also said that there are no fundamental
conflicts of interest existing between the two.
</P>
<P>
Wei said Austria will chair the EU in the latter half of this
year, a position filled on a rotating basis. He expressed his
belief that Austria will play a positive role in the long-term
development of Sino-Austrian and Sino-EU relations.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, Wei added, the further growth of party-to-party
relations will not only enhance mutual understanding, but will
also contribute to the development of state-to-state relations, as
well as the peace and stability of the world as a whole.
</P>
<P>
He went on to say that the CPC is willing to continue its
relations with the Austrian People's Party in line with the four
principles guiding party-to-party relations.
</P>
<P>
Khol praised China's achievements in reform and opening-up and
the monumental improvements in the living standards of Chinese
people.
</P>
<P>
He said Austria will extend great effort to ensure the
continuous growth of relations between the two countries and
between the EU and China during its term as rotating chairman of
the EU.
</P>
