Radio report said.
</P>
<P>
The Orient Radio said that at 1:40 am local time, Israeli
artillery began to fire mortar rounds on Majdel-Zewin and
Mansuli, about 50 kilometers south of the country's southern port
city of Saida and on the edge of the Israeli occupation zone.
</P>
<P>
