<HEADLINE> Local Insurance Company Doing Well in Shanghai </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, January 8 (Xinhua) -- The Tian'an Insurance Company,
the first regional property insurer in Shanghai's New Pudong Area,
has developed rapidly since its opening in October 1994.
</P>
<P>
