<HEADLINE> Argentina Sets Car Production And Sales Record </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUENOS AIRES, January 7 (Xinhua) -- Argentina hit record
figures both at production and exportation of automobiles over
1997, the Association of Auto Makers reported on Wednesday.
</P>
